---
title: Carb Smart Beef and Sweet Potato Salad with Creamy Herbed Sun-Dried Tomato Dressing
description: A generous drizzle of creamy, herby sun-dried tomato dressing is the star of this dish. Smoky beef is cooked and tossed with roasted sweet potatoes, tangy marinated cucumber and a salad topper for a meal that skimps on carbs, not flavour.

Carb Smart (50 g carbohydrates or less) is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.
